quran[9]{c,v,t}:
  6,36,"Anndu ko noototoo, ko …ìen nanoo…ìe. Maay…ìe …ìen, Alla Immintinoyay …ìe ; refti ko ka Makko …ìe ruttetee"
  6,37,"∆Åe wi'i : \"Ko hanno Aaya Jippinee e makko?\" Maaku : \"Alla ko Ha…óatan…óo nde O Jippinta Aaya. Kono …óuu…óu…ìe e ma…ì…ìe anndaa"
  6,38,"Alaa e ru…ìoowel ka leydi, wanaa wiirayndu wiirira gabiti=bibje mun …ói…ói, si wanaa ko mofte yeruuje mo'on. Men Accaali huunde ka Deftere. Refti ko ka Joomi ma…ì…ìe …ìe moo…ìoytee=rentite"
  6,39,"∆Åen fennu…ìe Aayeeje Amen …óen ko faa…óu…ìe mum…ìe e nder majjere. On mo Alla Muuyi majjinnde O Majjinay mo, on Mo O Muuyi O Wa…óay mo e laawol focciingol"
  6,40,"Maaku : \"Yeetee lam : si lepte Alla …óen arii on maa Darngal ngal arii on, e ko ko woori Alla noddoton, si on laatike goongu…ìe"
  6,41,"Si ko woni, ko Kanko noddoton, O Hunca kon ko noddirton Mo e mun, si O Muuyii, yejjiton ko sirkoton"
  6,42,"Gom…óii Men Nulii e mofte ado maa, Men Nanngiri …ìe sa…óteendde e lorra -belajo'o, …ìe yankinoto"
  6,43,"Ko hanno nde sa…óteende Amen nden arnoo …ìe, …ìe yankinoo ? Kono …ìer…óe ma…ì…ìe …óen yoorii, seytaane kadi cu…óinanii …ìe kon ko gollaynoo"
  6,44,"Nde …ìe yejjitunoo kon ko …ìe waajoraa, Men udditanno …ìe dame kala huunde ; haa nde …ìe weltori kon ko …ìe okkaa, Men Nanngiri …ìe juhal, e jaka ko …ìe ta∆¥ii…ìe"
